# ShellCheck configuration for this repo.
#
# Consumed by the render-dotfiles `shellcheck` CI job (ShellCheck walks up from
# each linted file to this repo-root file) and by any local `shellcheck` run.
# `.shellcheckrc` begins with a dot, so chezmoi never deploys it — repo-meta only.
#
# SC2016 "Expressions don't expand in single quotes": this repo deliberately
# wraps command / flag names in literal backticks inside single-quoted
# printf/echo diagnostics, e.g. a wrapper reporting that its required `jq`
# command is not on PATH. The backticks are intentional message formatting,
# never command substitution, and this style is used across many CLI wrappers
# and provisioning scripts, so the check is disabled repo-wide rather than
# suppressed line-by-line.
disable=SC2016
